Constraints
-defines relationship or limitation among data elements that the DBMS is required to enforce

-primary/unique keys
-foreign keys or referential-integrity
-attribute based constraints
-assertions: boolean SQL statement

Default: reject mods
Cascade: Make same changes in relation
set NULL: change to NULL

Delete Bud tuple from Beers

ON DELETE SET NULL
ON UPDATE CASCADE

Attribute Based Check
Tuple Based Check

Assertions

CREATE ASSERTION <name> CHECK (<condition>)
